1047
01:14:01,751 --> 01:14:04,811
<i>This court sentences you</i>
<i>to a prison term of five years...</i>

1048
01:14:04,887 --> 01:14:08,152
24 <i>months to be served</i>
<i>in a federal corrections institute...</i>

1049
01:14:08,224 --> 01:14:12,183
